title: Carlos Libedinsky - Narcotango 2 [FLAC]  + covers
description:
"Tango is burning
with passion, coexisting, struggling
and creating new ways of expression
in music and dance, like a delicate heartbeat
intimately tied to its roots, dramatically
and happily seduced by the present.
Tango is ardent 
and leaves a strong impression on our senses 
in every spot of the world. It is moving to be here to live it."

                                               Carlos Libedinsky


This is second disk of project "Narcotango". It's more quiet and melodic but still very energetic.
Disk is very interesting for me. First of all by impressive accordion music. Some sound effects in last track made me crszy first time =)

All pictures in booklet is 300 pixels/inch. All tracks are separate & with tags. Ripped by EAC.
If you want to burn this CD, you can download cole2K nero audio plugin (google helps you), or use alcohol, EAC  etc.
